   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>Create the chat entity in the CRM.</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Login to CRM using admin credentials</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click on the main menu and select <strong>Settings.</strong> <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 235px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_ec09a8a05c669e51db5d72f8937888830d34706300e1e0873057b44e98cb2666/Chat-entity.png?cb=0d5019d00817831c000f6952f166dd8b" alt="Chat-entity.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span></p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click on <strong>Customizations</strong>.&nbsp; <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 150px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_64e7bf094efd00d49e0e137048b7d8effa18e9b171af4fe7ee212b82d4985793/customizations.png?cb=3bdf3d395e6609b25437cfc5316c9a4c" alt="customizations.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span></p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click on <strong>Customize the System.</strong> The Entities page will open up. <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 150px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_d1c1a773740159951ae834994e6a715bd08dbec600959801f306fc4b97dc6533/Entities.png?cb=52e5225b906ac835aba88a021a52cada" alt="Entities.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span></p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click on <strong>Entities</strong> &amp; then click&nbsp;<strong>New. </strong>This&nbsp;will open the <strong>Entity-New</strong> Page. <span class="theme-inline-image"> <image-lightbox> <span class="inline-image" data-component="inline-image" data-use-text-height="false" style="--height: 150px;"> <img src="/__attachments/a_6b8c3522b8b22308be35f34fb51e2a020df76157da9da258c12f3343575f716f/NewEntity.png?cb=7e7b15a1f918d348c44e16a99a4bed23" alt="NewEntity.png" data-scope="internal"> </span> </image-lightbox> </span></p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Fill in the following fields on the <strong>Entity-New</strong> Page.</p>
  <div class="theme-table">
   <table-expand>
    <scroll-shadow>
     <table-sort>
      <div data-component="table" data-align="unset" data-number-column="false">
       <table>
        <colgroup>
         <col>
         <col>
        </colgroup>
        <tbody>
         <tr>
          <th>
           <p><strong>Field Name</strong></p>
          </th>
          <th>
           <p><strong>Data\Action</strong></p>
          </th>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <p>Display Name</p>
          </td>
          <td>
           <p>chat</p>
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <p>Plural Name</p>
          </td>
          <td>
           <p>Chat</p>
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <p>Name (<strong>Entity Name</strong>)</p>
          </td>
          <td>
           <p>*new_chat (<strong>new</strong> is prefix &amp; <strong>chat</strong> is name)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <p>Define as an activity entity</p>
          </td>
          <td>
           <p><strong>✓</strong></p>
          </td>
         </tr>
        </tbody>
       </table>
      </div>
     </table-sort>
    </scroll-shadow>
   </table-expand>
  </div>
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click on <strong>Save</strong> and close the <strong>Entity -New Page</strong>.</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click on <strong>Publish All Customizations</strong> on the entities page.</p>
 </li>
</ol>
<p>
 <br>
</p>
